item.title: CVE-2024-5766|2024-06-08T12:00:06.623Z -- n%2Fa -- likeshop
item.description: A vulnerability was found in Likeshop up to 2.5.7 and classified as problematic. This issue affects some unknown processing of the file /admin of the component Merchandise Handler. The manipulation leads to cross site scripting. The attack may be initiated remotely. The identifier VDB-267449 was assigned to this vulnerability. Eine problematische Schwachstelle wurde in Likeshop bis 2.5.7 gefunden. Hierbei geht es um eine nicht exakt ausgemachte Funktion der Datei /admin der Komponente Merchandise Handler.
